Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,莎珂 你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我從格奧爾格伯爵那裡聽到了所有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你為Headkeeper…不 為反帝派提供了幫助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,母親還活著嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能這麼相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不然我都不知道自己為了什麼幫助他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,活著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就在帝都 現在還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,傑德 你為什麼會在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有報告說你們回來了 而且不是去我那裡 而是回了老家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你們會在逮捕行動中都被抓起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,結果好像還被你們知道了很多閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你…用輝光之種殺了那麼多人?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一半是我 但另一半呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,果然…是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 雖然讓你們在監獄裡來個母女重逢也挺感人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但人質有一個就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊 我不是一直都乖乖聽你們的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,已經用不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,住…住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,還是動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…莎珂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事? 這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,咦? 怎麼了? 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…那是災禍之光?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,帝都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這是假貨?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,振作點 走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,站得起來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊走 大家有秩序地轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,難道…這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,光…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 接下來該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,「喔」你個頭啊 萊奧呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,卡雅 露 哈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不在? 他們去哪兒了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,已經去避難了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事啦 他肯定還活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那小子頑強得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊 肯定沒事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我們自己得先沒事才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可別真的死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你這樣子…是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,災禍之光…落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的…最後實驗的…集大成…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,其答案…和…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,和光…融合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,融合?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你也…你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,和光…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,融合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,現在要先幹什麼啊? 這個情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是預言的災難嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來還以為應該更晚一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦? 該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜點 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要去帝城嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,別說傻話了 那不是自殺嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,現在已經管不了什麼反帝派了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也是哦 那要去據點嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,沒時間了 想想格奧爾格伯爵說的那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,「搖籃」開始啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒時間了 城市會被封鎖的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…以努麥爾嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…以努麥爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,離開這裡吧 外面出事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…發生了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,以努麥爾?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧? 能…認得出我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,萊奧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,卡迪歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看這情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是沒法交流了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,從古泰爾到帝都這麼遠都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,到底嚴重到什麼地步? 完全想像不出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你們了 一定要沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 住手啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是萊奧卡迪歐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不認識我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,萊奧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,對 是萊奧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你不當人了嗎 以努麥爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你給我清醒點 以努麥爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,以努麥爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,送貨員以努麥爾·格勞納
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你認不出我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,認不…認…認不出…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是為什麼要回帝都的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,難道不是下定了某種決心回來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,決心?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,別胡鬧了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你個通緝犯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,通緝…通緝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,犯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你要給我找多少麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,才滿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了我大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還想連我也殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,變異?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是覺醒者?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,想…想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,希賽爾?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 認得出我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,萊奧卡迪歐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,終於恢復清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,站得起來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看來是不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這個…給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,答應…給浮士德的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,應該有治療雷火病的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一定會交給他的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…你會有這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 是希賽爾要我交給你的 結果我給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因為發生太多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 這東西算是救了我一命 就原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,搖籃會將帝都封鎖 到時候你就出不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:15:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…有什麼要對你妹妹希賽爾說的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥哥的事…很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,居然比我先到啊 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔…你居然還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是我要說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,以努麥爾和本呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,阿諾 現在能走了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒時間沮喪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,以努麥爾 你在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,在就回句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,以努麥爾 該醒醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,能從這地下通道出去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,難道地底下住著這種東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,差點就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,厲害啊…從來沒看到過這麼大規模的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,居然能把整個城市都封鎖起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們今後該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣根本聯繫不上同伴們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小子 你今後怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去找康拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他應該和我弟弟妹妹…還有希賽爾一起去避難了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去一趟新都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好 大叔我陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,借的裝備也得還回去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我覺得那已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那就出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不 別跟過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(918,995)}Wahrheit
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 迎接瓦爾海特帝國新的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真是慘啊 那道光落下才兩週就亂成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,無政府狀態 無法地帶 完全為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不過畢竟比那裡面要好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,阿諾德他們還活著嗎? 搞不好變成怪物了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.62,0:22:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真可憐 帝國軍也失去了指揮系統 分崩離析
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.29,0:22:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,傳說還有些不法之徒 打著帝國兵的名號當強盜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道康拉德和萊奧還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,保護好…一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}陛下…皇后…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.91,0:22:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這個孩子…求求你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.04,0:23:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 救救她吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這是皇族的紋章?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子叫什麼名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,蘿潔瑪麗…皇帝陛下的女兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你…照顧好她…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,「又」是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你還真是一個招來麻煩事的天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
